Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:57.23,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Lovers Quarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The wolf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:12.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then this is a threat from the Medioh Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling us to stay put until the dealings are complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,or else they'll take her to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:23.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's no guarantee that they won't take her there when they're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:29.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, we have already invested greatly in the weakening Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be at a serious loss if we drop out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us rescue your companion, and have you go into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If the church steps in and prosecutes us, {doesn't he say something about "confess" or about the Medioh reporting?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:44.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot do anything but act like docile sheep.{there will be nothing we can do except act like docile sheep}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot hide as long as you remain in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll escape with her outside the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're really lucky, you'll be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be prosecuted even if you take her to a different city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With the possible profit they can gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to settle this with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had a trump card that could counter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will file a complaint to the church
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Medioh Company has taken your companion and is bribing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But by doing so, it'll be problematic for them, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the worst, they'll bring unfavorable testimony against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:34.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest profit from the silver coins is the privileges we can receive from the King of Thoreni. {yes the case is right here, don't change "is" to "are" please}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,According to our research, the royal family is financially conservative right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They are planning to gather the circulating coins, break them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,lower the silver content, and increase the number of coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If ten coins become thirteen, there would be an extra three coins as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:04:00.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be more funds, but at the same time, the country's prestige would decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the long term, the drawbacks would have a greater effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Thoreni's royal family is willing to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,showing how much of a financial problem they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,depending on the negotiations, we can have first claim to the royal family's mining,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:20.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,military, tariff, and ruling rights, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Before Medioh prosecutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you finish the negotiations with the Thoreni silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and use the privileges as a negotiation card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we won't get all the privileges, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying to make them buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than taking you out and making them think that buying would solve this matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that the Medioh Company will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're holding on to a card that may cause us to be burned at the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Kingdom of Thoreni has a dispute with the church, they won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive that they wouldn't want it to be known that they did business
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,, with a company that could cause them to be burned as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If the church turns its eyes toward us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll think of us as the main perpetrators for the dealings and treat us as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:14.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Medioh Company won't make any accusations that would provoke the king's malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:19.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, but even so, I'm sure they won't give up quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is forced double suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:27.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll add your companion as a condition for the privileges, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's methodically sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is too difficult. {TLC suggestion - but there are too many difficulties to it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,From my guess, the Medioh Company hasn't accumulated many silver coins yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your basis for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If they {\i1}did{\i0} have enough coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they would have taken Horo to the church when they captured her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:57.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they made it so that we wouldn't take action because of their lack in confidence. {dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dealing that will take advantage of the King's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they will do anything showy to resolve this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:08.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do, Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:13.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take Horo back and keep running until the negotiations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:19.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't run, I believe I will be able to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:22.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, you should gather coins and attend the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you have Horo persecuted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have an unfavorable testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:34.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you will cooperate, I will be able to escape in one or two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The incarnation of the wolf deity will be running away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:43.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If she uses her abilities, humans won't be able to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:51.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think it will take you to accumulate enough coins in order to negotiate with the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:01.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let a horse go now, it will arrive at Thoreni Castle by sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming that the king makes a prompt decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they should be back by dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you don't know the amount of coins you have accumulated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The negotiations will be done with an optimistic calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can prepare it by the day of approval, there should be no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, will we be able to get a prompt decision from the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:27.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ever felt like it, we could get a prompt decision from any negotiation.  {edit plz}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have you have found out where Horo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Milone Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have people in the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:44.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stores catching on fire is an everyday occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:47.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why our preventive measures in the town are flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have one rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The church?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:56.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a stronger presence than we do in many countries and cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:00.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time calls for preparation, they are surprisingly well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If the church were to become serious and begin a search,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't be able to run and would have no choice but to isolate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:14.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to know who was backing the Medioh Company before heading into negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:18.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew who it was, we could find their paper trail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and be able to seize all their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for your safety and success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely answer your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The codeword is "Perion and Numai."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The two big gold coins, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good omen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:43.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I go underground, I place my hand on the right wall and advance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:47.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and your destination is at the end of the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo will be in the storehouse above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal will be the ringing of the town's bells,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and the operation to rescue her will begin at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're successful, the cover above will open up and your companion will drop down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:07.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hear them say "Rahei," wait for my companions to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:12.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hear "Perouso," you two run away by yourselves using the path we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rahei" and "Perouso."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Booms and recessions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to remember, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Go down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they've prepared this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that the church made underground passages
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,for the passing of information and tax evasion while saying they were digging tombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, we're changing locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray this situation won't call for the use of edged or blunted weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why am I shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:27.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:43.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rahei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rahei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:49.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Numai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:51.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Perion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to take these and go down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go down unless you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours, so take it and let's head up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Perion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:15.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Numai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What an astonishing partner you have for your trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one more with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:36.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll take care of the trail and come up from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After giving information on the Medioh Company to my companions, we will leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad I'm safe, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Say my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Horo the Wise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:18.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can name everyone who has brought me shame for as long as I've lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:21.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I have to add a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:28.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you would come for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:34.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I had clearly thought that you would come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it is annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:45.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, shouldn't you take up arms and fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:49.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to go in that hole, and because of that, I was needlessly ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're safe now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:13.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die as long as you keep those grains of wheat, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:19.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A human male would fall for me right away, since I'm cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:23.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's no fit partner for me among human males.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:27.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell them, "If you touch me, something'll fall off,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they all turn white with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She appeared there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think was there among my captors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:48.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from Pasroe Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:00.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she heard my name from that youngster, Zeiren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was simply folklore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She lives inside the village's wheat field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:20.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs39}The incarnation of the wolf deity can manipulate the outcome of the harvest to become abundant or poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:25.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many years I had lived on that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be more than the furs on my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for there to be an abundant harvest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:37.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be years where I would have to let the land rest and produce a poor harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it was within my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have become a better land to produce wheat than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they treated me as the deity that brings abundant harvest, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was most likely because of their farming rather than my meddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who cut the last bunch of wheat would get caught by everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think she said to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She had thought that it might have been me after hearing my name from Zeiren. {dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pathetic, but I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She continued, and said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:32.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The era of us following your moods is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:36.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to be fearful of your whims anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:44.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hand you over to the church and break away from the old era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so vexed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all how you think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:31.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You would've had to leave the land either way, since you want to return to the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want your back hairs pulled on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,then just kick the sand at them with your hind legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot better that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't just leave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:46.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, no, {\i1}we're{\i0} merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Profit alone or whatever will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We laugh when the money comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We cry when we become bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i0} will laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:07.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:12.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a proper conversation in several hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My emotions are brittle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time I've cried in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need to cry in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what I'm trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only with you to earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:34.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to run away until the Milone Company contacts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep crying like that, it'll be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't need to cry in front of you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl's specialty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you two finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The one backing the Medioh Company is Count Eiren Dotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant who traded wheat with the the Count
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,, overheard that he was collecting a large amount of silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell this to Marhait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:18.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess people who bring us business proposals are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean these ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd become a merchant again after looking at you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better if you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You might pick up someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A wagon for a single trader is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish and hope that someone like her will come my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:45.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through some terrible experiences after you picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm cute that way too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty cute man yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:19.97,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:25.35,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:33.27,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.83,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:41.26,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:46.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.93,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.62,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:02.58,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:07.67,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:10.24,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.68,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.54,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:18.89,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:23.18,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:29.07,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:32.72,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:43.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Silent Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Silent Farewell.
